metadata.description: "Desert Solitude" is an exploration of my love for crystals, architecture, being one with nature, escaping technology and becoming ok with the idea of being alone. metadata.name: Balanced #105
metadata.description:
What does balance look like when viewed through the lens of pure mathematics? This is the question Balanced attempts to answer.

Each output is composed of a unique collection of blocks mathematically stacked to be in perfect balance.

This is my Genesis project. Enjoy!

Interactions:
1 - Reverse your stack vertically and re-balance.
2 - Toggle between square and portrait frame.
3 - Show center of mass. 
4 - Toggle the border.
5 - Toggle the background (color/transparent)
6 - Export image (2048x2048)
7 - Export image (4096x4096)
8 - Export image (8192x8192)

How it was made: https://www.jeffweber.art/balanced

metadata.name: Hatch Field 002 #181
metadata.description:
P5js drawing on fx(hash). Experimenting with translating recent work in done in Grasshopper exploring hatch patterns to p5.js. By Andrew Kudless / Matsys @matsysdesign
There are five feature groups:
- Base Hue: Red, Orange, Yellow, Spring Green, Green, Ocean Green, Cyan, Sky Blue, Blue, Purple, Magenta, and Crimson. Each has the same random chance of being the base color (12%).
- Hue Range: Narrow (14%), Wide (51%), and Infinite(34%)
- Lineweight: Thin (5%), Medium (10%), Thick (10%), Extra Thick (75%)
- Fray: Loose (90%), Tight (10%)
- Wind: Eastern Hurricane (10%), Eastern Gale (10%), Eastern Breeze (20%), Calm (20%), Western Breeze (20%), Western Gale (10%), Western Hurricane (10%)

metadata.name: Window gratings #36
metadata.description:
Window gratings were once a ubiquitous sight in Taiwan. Starting around the 1950s, homeowners began installing stylized metal barriers in front of their windows to keep out thieves.

The artwork focused on window gratings and add some fantastic colors & materials.
Wait for seconds and you'll see time flies.

100,000 possible buildings & floors combinations  
20 different color palette + 20 monotone (20%)
9 unique Window grating styles
6 door styles
4 roof and 4 fence styles
3 room styles

[keyboard] Press 's' to save PNG in original size
